<p>The text in the following buttons should be underlined.</p>
<u><p class=inline><u><button>foo</button><input type=button value=foo></u><u><button>foo</button><input type=button value=foo></u><u><button><u>foo</u></button><input type=button value=foo></u><u><button>foo</button><input type=button value=foo></u><u><button>foo</button><input type=button value=foo></u></p></u>
<p>The text in the following buttons should NOT be underlined.</p>
<p class=inline-block><u><button>foo</button><input type=button value=foo></u></p>
